text: Anneloes van Veen (born 7 August 1990) is a Dutch competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of the Netherlands Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
